## Ethical Participation  
All contributors must adhere to our [Code of Conduct](CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md).  
Violations may result in license termination under Section 4(c) of the MIT License. 

## Ethical Use Covenant (Non-Legal Guidance)
Users are ethically encouraged to:
1. Avoid applications violating human rights principles
2. Refrain from military/weapons system development
3. Consider environmental impact assessments
